{"tid":1604798,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"無障礙的士預約費 5年翻倍至$120","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T05:32:20.000Z","uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9c307c38e1f98c5264f8953e7a457baa807903","tid":1604798,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"「現時殘疾人士乘坐一般公共交通工具每程收費為兩元，惟的士截然不同。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有提供無障礙的士服務的營辦商將於下月起調高預約服務費，價格在五年翻倍。</span></span>輪椅人士與關注團體同斥加價令殘疾人士百上加斤，批評政府未有機制監管營辦公司，令基層輪椅人士難有更多選擇。<br />\n<br />\n無障礙的士收費不一，有額外需支付預約費、有按行程報價、亦有設下最低消費，動輒過百元起跳。有提供預約無障礙的士服務的公司更將於十月一日提高預約費用，收費一百二十元。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搵鬼搭咩dllm <br />\n一call的士百二蚊<br />\n垃圾政府就係咁撚樣<br />\n一日啲官未殘疾就唔知殘疾人士苦處<br />\n腦殘另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WqsB2kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqsB2kd.jpg&h=4b7b6093&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNoYwdy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNoYwdy.jpg&h=1ba67a43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8S00Kyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8S00Kyz.jpg&h=42f8cc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MW2FKyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMW2FKyA.jpg&h=ce8632c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxmOTrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxmOTrV.jpg&h=8540e858&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dpa4rMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpa4rMW.jpg&h=1e99e365&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}